  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Village Montana Apartments are self catering apartments. Each apartment has an equipped kitchenette, with the resort centre being a short walk away. The residence has its own bakery delivery service available to book and pay for locally. </p>
<p>Alternatively, we've partnered up with Huski who provide premium oven ready meals across the French Alps. Huski will deliver your meals directly to your accommodation in time for your arrival, all you'll have to do is cook. If you'd like to know more, please click <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/huski-food-drink-delivery-service" target="_blank">here</a> for further details.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Village Montana is made up of three residences, Montana Premier and Valbel both located on the piste and Montana Soleil is just over the road, so all of the apartments are conveniently positioned. The apartments are spacious, comfortable and all have superb views across <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a>. The resort centre is accessed by a lift and a covered walkway, plus you can enjoy how convenient the complex is with on-site restaurants, bar, lounge, sun terrace and gift shop. There is also a bakery delivery service, taking the fuss out of breakfast (pay locally).</p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p><span>Val Thorens is a high-altitude ski resort in the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys</a>, and most of our apartments have direct access to the slopes and ski lifts, </span><span></span>allowing you to start and end your ski day right at your doorstep. The residence also has its own onsite bar, lounge and restaurant, so you don't need to go far to meet friends and family for a drink or bite to eat. The resort centre is easily accessible by a lift and covered walk way, where you can find plenty of shops, bars and restaurants - perfect for the days when you don't feel like cooking. </p>
<h2><span>Well equipped ski apartments</span></h2>
<p>The apartments can vary in size and layout, accommodating different group sizes, however each apartment is equipped with everything you need for a relaxing stay in the mountains including a balcony with scenic views, comfortable bedrooms and an open-plan lounge and equipped kitchenette. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
