  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One Bedroom Soleil Apartments</strong> sleep two to three people and are around 32m². These apartments have a living room with a single sofa bed and a twin bedroom and one bathroom. These apartments are located in the Montana Soleil building. </p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Premier</strong><strong> Cabin Apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 35m². These apartments have a twin bedroom, an alcove with bunk beds, and one bathroom (may have a separate WC). These apartments are located in the Montana Premier building.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Soleil Apartments</strong> sleep up to four people and are around 45m². These apartments have two twin bedrooms, and one bathroom. These apartments are located in the Montana Soleil building.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Cabin Soleil Apartments</strong> sleep up to six people and are around 49m². These apartments have two twin bedrooms,  a cabin room with bunkbeds, one bathroom with a bath, one shower room and a separate toilet. These apartments are located in the Montana Soleil building. </p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Premium Valbel Apartments </strong>sleep two to four people and are around 45m². These apartments have been renovated in recent years, and have two bedrooms, and one bathroom.  These apartments are located in the Valbel building.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Beds are made upon arrival, towels are provided with a midweek change on request and end of stay cleaning is included (except the kitchen - bins must be taken out to the main outside bin area. </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Lounge area </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Fully equipped kitchenette with hotplates, oven, fridge, microwave, kettle, toaster, kitchenware and dishwasher</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Satellite TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Towels and bed linen</li>
<li><span>Raclette machines, fondue set, DVD player, board games etc are available on loan (subject to availability)</span></li>
<li><span>Additional beds are available for a supplement</span></li>
</ul>
<p>The Village Montana is made up of three different residences: Montana Premier and Valbel (which both have pisteside locations) and Montana Soleil, just over the road.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
